item.title: Need help making a 667-711
item.dc:creator: @svrking27 svrking27
item.description:
@svrking27 wrote:

ok first u want ur things to look like this

compiler:
@echo off
echo Compiling
“C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.7.0_05/bin/javac.exe” -d bin -cp lib/; -sourcepath src src/com/rs/.java
“C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.7.0_05/bin/javac.exe” -d bin -cp lib/; -sourcepath src src/com/rs/game/npc/familiar/.java
echo Complete
pause

runbat:
@echo off
title runserver
“C:/Program Files/Java/jre7/bin/java.exe” -Xmx512m -cp bin;lib/*; com.rs.Launcher true true false
pause

compile and run
